      </div>
      <!-- Text bucket -->
      <div class="half-block">
        <div class="text-block flex-column flex-center">
          <h1 id="working-with-the-community-ac5c">Working with the community</h1>

<p>Our staff and students are involved with the community in and around Bath, including partnerships with community groups and collaborations with local organisations.</p>

<p>We support local students to prepare for their future, working with their schools and colleges to inspire them to pursue further study and careers.</p>

<p>Find out more about <a href="/topics/our-place-in-the-community/">Our place in the community</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
