        <!-- / Pinned items -->
      </div>
      <!-- Text bucket -->
      <div class="half-block">
        <div class="text-block flex-column flex-center">
          <h1 id="reducing-our-environmental-impact-94be">Reducing our environmental impact</h1>

<p>We're reducing our environmental impact through ethical food sourcing, waste management, generating our own sustainable energy, and raising awareness of how staff and students can help. We work with the local community, industry, public sector bodies and third sector organisations, to support the transition to the net zero carbon economy.</p>

<p><a href="/topics/climate-change-and-the-university-of-bath/">Find out more about how we're reducing our carbon footprint</a>. </p>
        </div>
